<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="el">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Noëta — Αναφορά Γλωσσικού Ελέγχου</title>
{# Fonts: loaded from CDN for HTML preview; WeasyPrint uses @font-face fallback below #}
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Newsreader:ital,opsz,wght@0,6..72,400;0,6..72,500;0,6..72,600;1,6..72,400&family=DM+Sans:opsz,wght@9..40,400;9..40,500;9..40,600;9..40,700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root{
    --paper:#FBFAF7;
    --ink:#1C1B19;
    --ink-soft:#6B6760;
    --ink-faint:#9A958C;
    --rule:#E5E1D8;
    --rule-soft:#EFEBE2;
    --accent:#8A2B26;
    --del:#A8453C;
    --del-bg:#F8ECEA;
    --ins:#3F6B4F;
    --ins-bg:#EAF1EB;
    --sev-high:#9A2C24;
    --sev-mid:#9A6A1E;
    --sev-low:#6B6760;
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box;}
  html,body{margin:0;padding:0;background:#EDEAE3;}
  body{
    font-family:"DM Sans",-apple-system,system-ui,sans-serif;
    color:var(--ink);
    -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
    line-height:1.5;
  }
  .page{
    max-width:820px;
    margin:32px auto;
    background:var(--paper);
    padding:60px 64px 48px;
    box-shadow:0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.06),0 14px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.10);
  }

  /* ---------- Masthead ---------- */
  .masthead{
    display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;
    padding-bottom:22px;border-bottom:2px solid var(--ink);
  }
  .brand{display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:10px;}
  .wordmark{
    font-family:"Newsreader",serif;font-weight:600;font-size:30px;
    letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--ink);line-height:1;
  }
  .wordmark .dot{color:var(--accent);}
  .brand-tag{
    font-family:"JetBrains Mono",monospace;font-size:9.5px;font-weight:500;
    text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.18em;color:var(--ink-faint);
  }
  .eyebrow{
    font-family:"JetBrains Mono",monospace;font-size:10px;font-weight:500;
    text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.2em;color:var(--accent);
    text-align:right;
  }
  .issued{
    font-family:"JetBrains Mono",monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--ink-faint);
    text-align:right;margin-top:4px;
  }

  /* ---------- Document title ---------- */
  .doc-title{
    font-family:"Newsreader",serif;font-weight:500;font-size:26px;
    line-height:1.25;margin:26px 0 4px;letter-spacing:-.01em;
  }
  .doc-sub{
    font-family:"Newsreader",serif;font-style:italic;font-size:15px;
    color:var(--ink-soft);
  }

  /* ---------- Metadata strip ---------- */
  .meta{
    display:flex;gap:0;margin:26px 0 0;border-top:1px solid var(--rule);
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--rule);
  }
  .meta-cell{
    flex:1;padding:14px 0;text-align:center;
    border-right:1px solid var(--rule-soft);
  }
  .meta-cell:last-child{border-right:none;}
  .meta-num{
    font-family:"Newsreader",serif;font-size:25px;font-weight:500;line-height:1;
  }
  .meta-num.accent{color:var(--accent);}
  .meta-label{
    font-family:"JetBrains Mono",monospace;font-size:9px;text-transform:uppercase;
    letter-spacing:.13em;color:var(--ink-faint);margin-top:7px;
  }

  /* ---------- Section heading ---------- */
  .section-head{
    display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin:40px 0 18px;
  }
  .section-head h2{
    font-family:"JetBrains Mono",monospace;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;
    text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.16em;color:var(--ink-soft);margin:0;
    white-space:nowrap;
  }
  .section-head .line{flex:1;height:1px;background:var(--rule);}

  /* ---------- Category breakdown ---------- */
  .cats{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:11px;}
  .cat-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:150px 1fr 34px;align-items:center;gap:14px;}
  .cat-name{font-size:13.5px;font-weight:500;color:var(--ink);}
  .cat-bar{height:7px;background:var(--rule-soft);border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden;}
  .cat-fill{height:100%;background:var(--accent);opacity:.85;border-radius:4px;}
  .cat-count{
    font-family:"JetBrains Mono",monospace;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;
    text-align:right;color:var(--ink);
  }

  /* ---------- Empty state ---------- */
  .empty-state{
    padding:32px 0;text-align:center;
    font-family:"Newsreader",serif;font-style:italic;
    font-size:16px;color:var(--ink-faint);
  }

  /* ---------- Correction entries ---------- */
  .entry{
    display:grid;grid-template-columns:64px 1fr;gap:22px;
    padding:22px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--rule-soft);
    page-break-inside:avoid;
  }
  .entry:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
  .rail{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:9px;padding-top:2px;}
  .rail .num{
    font-family:"Newsreader",serif;font-size:21px;font-weight:500;
    color:var(--ink-faint);line-height:1;
  }
  .rail .para{
    font-family:"JetBrains Mono",monospace;font-size:10px;font-weight:500;
    color:var(--ink-soft);
  }
  .badge{
    display:inline-block;font-family:"JetBrains Mono",monospace;font-size:8.5px;
    font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;
    padding:3px 6px;border-radius:3px;width:fit-content;
  }
  .badge.sev-high{color:var(--sev-high);background:#F6E7E5;}
  .badge.sev-mid{color:var(--sev-mid);background:#F6EEDD;}
  .badge.sev-low{color:var(--sev-low);background:#ECE9E2;}

  .body .cat-tag{
    font-family:"JetBrains Mono",monospace;font-size:9.5px;font-weight:600;
    text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.11em;color:var(--accent);
    margin-bottom:9px;
  }
  .context{
    font-family:"Newsreader",serif;font-size:17px;line-height:1.65;
    color:var(--ink);margin:0 0 11px;
  }
  .context del{
    text-decoration:line-through;text-decoration-color:var(--del);
    text-decoration-thickness:1.5px;color:var(--del);
    background:var(--del-bg);padding:0 3px;border-radius:2px;
  }
  .context ins{
    text-decoration:none;color:var(--ins);font-weight:500;
    background:var(--ins-bg);padding:0 3px;border-radius:2px;margin-left:3px;
  }
  .note{
    font-size:13px;line-height:1.55;color:var(--ink-soft);
    padding-left:13px;border-left:2px solid var(--rule);
  }

  /* ---------- Teaser row ---------- */
  .teaser-row{
    padding:18px 0;text-align:center;border-bottom:1px solid var(--rule-soft);
    font-family:"Newsreader",serif;font-style:italic;font-size:15px;color:var(--ink-faint);
  }

  /* ---------- Footer / CTA ---------- */
  .footer{
    margin-top:44px;padding-top:22px;border-top:2px solid var(--ink);
    display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-end;gap:24px;
  }
  .cta-text{font-family:"Newsreader",serif;font-size:15.5px;line-height:1.5;color:var(--ink);max-width:60%;}
  .cta-text strong{font-weight:600;color:var(--accent);}
  .foot-mark{text-align:right;}
  .foot-mark .wm{font-family:"Newsreader",serif;font-weight:600;font-size:17px;}
  .foot-mark .wm .dot{color:var(--accent);}
  .foot-mark .url{
    font-family:"JetBrains Mono",monospace;font-size:9.5px;color:var(--ink-faint);
    letter-spacing:.05em;margin-top:3px;
  }

  @media print{
    html,body{background:#fff;}
    .page{margin:0;max-width:none;box-shadow:none;padding:0;}
    @page{size:A4;margin:18mm 16mm;}
  }
  @media(max-width:680px){
    .page{padding:34px 24px;}
    .meta{flex-wrap:wrap;}
    .meta-cell{flex:1 1 50%;border-bottom:1px solid var(--rule-soft);}
    .cat-row{grid-template-columns:120px 1fr 30px;}
    .entry{grid-template-columns:48px 1fr;gap:14px;}
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">

  <!-- Masthead -->
  <header class="masthead">
    <div>
      <div class="brand">
        <span class="wordmark">Noëta<span class="dot">.</span></span>
      </div>
      <div class="brand-tag">Γλωσσικός έλεγχος κειμένων</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="eyebrow">Αναφορά Διορθώσεων</div>
      <div class="issued">{{ document.issued_date }} · {{ document.ref }}</div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Document title -->
  <h1 class="doc-title">{{ document.title }}</h1>
  <p class="doc-sub">{{ document.subtitle }}</p>

  <!-- Metadata -->
  <div class="meta">
    <div class="meta-cell">
      <div class="meta-num">{{ document.word_count }}</div>
      <div class="meta-label">Λέξεις</div>
    </div>
    <div class="meta-cell">
      <div class="meta-num">{{ document.paragraph_count }}</div>
      <div class="meta-label">Παράγραφοι</div>
    </div>
    <div class="meta-cell">
      <div class="meta-num accent">{{ document.total_corrections }}</div>
      <div class="meta-label">Διορθώσεις</div>
    </div>
    <div class="meta-cell">
      <div class="meta-num">{{ document.density }}</div>
      <div class="meta-label">Ανά 1.000 λέξεις</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Summary -->
  <div class="section-head"><h2>Σύνοψη ανά κατηγορία</h2><span class="line"></span></div>
  {% if categories %}
  <div class="cats">
    {% for cat in categories %}
    <div class="cat-row">
      <span class="cat-name">{{ cat.name }}</span>
      <div class="cat-bar"><div class="cat-fill" style="width:{{ cat.bar_pct }}%"></div></div>
      <span class="cat-count">{{ cat.count }}</span>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
  {% else %}
  <p class="empty-state">Δεν εντοπίστηκαν διορθώσεις.</p>
  {% endif %}

  <!-- Detailed corrections -->
  <div class="section-head"><h2>Αναλυτικές διορθώσεις</h2><span class="line"></span></div>

  {% if entries %}
    {% for entry in entries %}
    <div class="entry">
      <div class="rail">
        <span class="num">{{ entry.num }}</span>
        {% if entry.paragraph %}<span class="para">¶ {{ entry.paragraph }}</span>{% endif %}
        <span class="badge sev-{{ entry.severity }}">{{ entry.severity_label }}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="body">
        <div class="cat-tag">{{ entry.category }}</div>
        <p class="context">{{ entry.context_before | e }}<del>{{ entry.original | e }}</del><ins>{{ entry.corrected | e }}</ins>{{ entry.context_after | e }}</p>
        {% if entry.note %}<p class="note">{{ entry.note | e }}</p>{% endif %}
      </div>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}

    {% if teaser_enabled and hidden_count > 0 %}
    <div class="teaser-row">
      + {{ hidden_count }} ακόμη διορθώσεις — διαθέσιμες στο <strong>Noëta</strong>
    </div>
    {% endif %}

  {% else %}
  <p class="empty-state">Δεν εντοπίστηκαν διορθώσεις.</p>
  {% endif %}

  <!-- Footer / CTA -->
  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="cta-text">
      Η παρούσα αναφορά παρουσιάζει τις διορθώσεις. Στο περιβάλλον του <strong>Noëta</strong> εφαρμόζονται αυτόματα — με αποδοχή ανά διόρθωση ή εξαγωγή σε Word με παρακολούθηση αλλαγών.
    </div>
    <div class="foot-mark">
      <div class="wm">Noëta<span class="dot">.</span></div>
    </div>
  </footer>

</div>
</body>
</html>
